text.tspan: Milligrams of total antibiotic use per kilogram of livestock. This is adjusted for differences in livestock numbers
and species by standardizing to a population-corrected unit (PCU).
Note: Several small island states have been excluded as they are large anomalous outliers in the global dataset.
